byline.original: Special to THE NEW YORK TIMES

abstract: Gets anniv gift of guns from Pa Univ
snippet: PHILADELPHIA, Nov. 1--A gift of fifty guns and ammunition was made today to Eton College, England, by members of the University of Pennsylvania Rifle Club and officials of the university....

headline.main: U. OF P. GROUP GIVES FIFTY GUNS TO ETON; Students and Faculty Members Aid British Home Defense

lead_paragraph: PHILADELPHIA, Nov. 1--A gift of fifty guns and ammunition was made today to Eton College, England, by members of the University of Pennsylvania Rifle Club and officials of the university.
